name: 25 Hashes
description: I (@mathmakesart) created a Python program for turning strings into generative pixelart. Starting on 2021/03/12 I created 25 unique pixelart patterns, made from ETH addresses and transaction hashes submitted by the community. This image displays all 25 original pieces at full resolution in a 5-by-5 grid, for a total of 8000 by 8000 pixels. You can view the original tweet here: https://twitter.com/mathMakesArt/status/1370339297279279107
